Title: Stepping Down as .NET Cambridge Community Leader – Productive C#
Description: Today, I have sent the following email to the .NET Cambridge community members. It was a tough decision, and I am full of emotions typing this. Still, I firmly believe the time has come for me to give other people the opportunity to lead, allowing me to focus my energy on new goals for my professional career and life. It’s been a blast! Please get in touch with me if you’re interested in leading the community forward.
